Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.56,0:00:04.73,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,A Metamon joined us aboard the ship!{[A] Metamon became a nakama of this ship!}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.73,0:00:07.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’s a strange little critter{one} \N who can transform.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.11,0:00:11.62,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya seems happy \N to have found a new friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.62,0:00:14.45,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I hope all the rest of us \N can get along with it, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.50,0:00:19.29,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Yo-ssu! Spinnin’-‘n’-groovin’!{090}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.29,0:00:22.38,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,All you Pokémon Trainers out there! \N Comin’ in for a min?{090}{minmin}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.38,0:00:25.71,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Today I’ve got a livestream for ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.22,0:00:37.98,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,I’ll be responding to all y’all’s requests, \N so bring on the comments!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.98,0:00:39.10,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.73,0:00:45.28,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Let’s take a min to get jammin’! Woo-hoo!{minmin}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.45,0:00:55.91,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Huh? I can’t get it off... \N Dekanuchan, just sit still for a sec!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.89,0:01:17.10,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,All right!
Comment: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:56.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.47,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,This one’s rusty...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.47,0:03:18.34,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Maybe we should \N swap it for a new one.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.01,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,Nicely spotted, there. \N Good stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.68,0:03:24.60,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,A new bolt, a new bolt...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.60,0:03:28.73,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,Huh? That’s odd, \N I was {\i1}sure{\i0} I put one in here...{number unspecified in JP, I did put it/them/etc in here}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.99,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Oh... Is that it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.99,0:03:38.36,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,Right you are. There it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.91,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,Wait, it’s {\i1}huge!{\i0}
Comment: 10,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.20,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.17,0:03:52.88,Main,Molly,0,0,0,,No need to fret. I’ll apply a little cream to it, \N and you’ll be better in no time.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.38,0:03:55.09,Main,Molly,0,0,0,,Let’s see...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.63,Main,Molly,0,0,0,,There.
Comment: 10,0:04:01.89,0:04:02.68,Main,Molly,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.27,0:04:08.14,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Mawhip whipped cream!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.19,0:04:10.90,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.49,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Give it a good whisk...
Comment: 10,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.57,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.03,0:04:25.41,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Gettin’ pranked by Metamon! \N That’s so lame!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.83,0:04:29.46,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hoo... I laughed so hard, \N my mouth’s all dry! Water, water...
Comment: 10,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.04,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Comment: 10,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.88,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Grr!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.88,0:04:37.84,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.80,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,You shouldn’t play too many pranks!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.35,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I wonder {\i1}why{\i0} Metamon’s playing pranks.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.35,0:04:50.69,Main,Molly,0,0,0,,It’ll take some time \N for us to understand its feelings.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.44,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Dot? What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.44,0:04:59.03,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Ugh... I accidentally \N put a black mark on Gurumin’s legacy... {I accidentally created a black history(as in, ashamed past) for Gurumin...}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.28,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Dot!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.16,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,That was the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.62,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Miniguru!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.12,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Miniguru...?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.71,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,The Mini Gurumin \N that was on your stream!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.71,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Everyone’s calling it Miniguru \N and getting really excited!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.13,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,“Miniguru’s cute”...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.97,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,“I wanna see more Miniguru”...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.13,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.76,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Don’t tell me... \N Were {\i1}you{\i0} Miniguru, Metamon?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,S... So ca-yute!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.53,Main,Molly,0,0,0,,Ooh, it really is cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.65,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,It looks like doughy bread!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.78,Main,Molly,0,0,0,,How, exactly?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.78,0:05:42.41,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Bread!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.91,0:05:47.41,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Dot! Wouldn’t this be great for \N that bread festival I told you about before?{not Fred's 'mention'}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.37,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Oh, the Bread Fest.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.50,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Bread Fest?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.50,0:05:51.96,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.92,0:05:56.38,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,A bread festival \N where all sorts of bakers get together.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.38,0:06:02.55,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,{\q2}Apparently a bakery named Bakery Tongri-La uploaded \N a Gurumin bread to {SNS}social media, and it went viral.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.22,0:06:07.05,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,And you got a request for Gurumin \N to come liven the Fest up.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.05,0:06:10.06,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,A request, as in... a job?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.06,0:06:15.19,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,There’s gonna be a huge crowd, \N so I {\i1}was{\i0} planning to turn it down, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.19,0:06:21.36,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you appear with Miniguru, \N you’ll really liven things up {\i1}and{\i0} bring joy to Gurumin fans!{please line}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.03,0:06:26.20,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Dot should be in charge \N of what jobs Gurumin takes!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.66,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Gurumin and Miniguru \N appearing in a Bread Fest would be...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.87,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m not really...{sense-wise 'whoa that'd be so great to see... uh but I'm not that interested or anything, totally not drooling over the idea, it should be up to you}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.91,0:06:38.04,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Gurumin and Miniguru \N at a Bread Fest... Bread!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.42,0:06:42.34,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Gurubread! Minbread! Ahh...!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.39,0:06:50.43,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.27,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,If it’d bring joy to even a single fan, \N maybe I should do it. {please line}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.98,0:06:58.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Bread? Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.19,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Yo-ssu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.57,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Spinnin’-‘n’-groovin’!{090}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.86,0:07:10.62,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Metamon, c’mon! \N Ya gotta turn into Miniguru, just like before!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.16,0:07:17.21,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,I was hoping to rehearse it together,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.21,0:07:21.38,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,but if you won’t turn into Miniguru, \N maybe I should turn down the Bread Fest...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.05,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.05,0:07:22.63,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.72,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What are you doing down there?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.72,0:07:31.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I simply couldn’t {\i1}dare{\i0} to watch \N Gurumin and Miniguru’s rehearsal up close...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.93,0:07:36.10,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But if Metamon doesn’t want \N to transform into Miniguru,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.10,0:07:39.65,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,then about that, there is nothing \N to be done which we may do...{Liko garbled keigo overloaded from thoughts of bread, 'then that can't be helped' raised ~3 levels of politeness to the point it contradicts itself}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.65,0:07:45.40,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,NyahojaSuperfan! \N Thanks for always supporting me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.41,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{わぁ…！ }Gurumin!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.41,0:07:52.66,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,I’ll be relying \N on your continued support, y’hear!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.08,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Miniguru!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.08,0:08:03.25,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That’s one incredible move, \N letting it transform like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.09,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hmph! Ain’t nothin’ special!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.55,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I’ll show ya an awesome one {\i1}we{\i0} know!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.51,0:08:14.06,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Can you move like this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.06,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Deadly... Shadow Cross!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.06,0:08:19.31,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Nyoom, nyoom, nyoom, nyoom...!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.07,0:08:25.69,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ahh! It turned back!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.49,0:08:33.33,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Let’s eat some tasty Gurumin bread, \N and all {\i1}Gurumin{\i0} together, y’hear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.09,0:08:53.14,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,We’re gonna perform \N a Miniguru Dance for all my fans!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.47,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Let’s get practicing!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.27,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,A Miniguru Dance?! I wanna watch!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.27,0:09:00.39,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But I don’t wanna spoil \N my anticipation for the real show...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.94,0:09:04.98,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Miniguru, Miniguru, Minigur—!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.98,0:09:08.44,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Ooh! Great stuff, great stuff! \N Now you’ve started jammin’-min’!{minmin}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.15,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Gotta see it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.57,0:09:13.16,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Spinny-spinny! Mini-mini! \N Mini-mini! Spinny-spinny!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.87,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.12,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.41,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I can’t see!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.38,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Good work today, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.13,0:09:33.14,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Feels like this Mini Gurumin stuff \N is starting to take shape. {probably the routine + relevant wording take shape for a transforming mon}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.14,0:09:37.64,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Nyoom-nyoom-nyoom-nyoom...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.60,0:09:43.15,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,But if it laughs, the transformation wears off \N and it turns back to Metamon, eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.15,0:09:47.65,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Ult! Don’t you even {\i1}think{\i0} about \N doing that during the real show!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.86,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,In the end, I didn’t get to \N see the Miniguru Dance...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.70,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? What? \N Masquernya, what’s wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.33,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Before the event begins... {reordered from TL}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.33,0:10:10.17,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,...I’ve gotta go say hi to Bakery Tongri-La’s manager, \N who put in the request for me to attend!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.17,0:10:14.13,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Gurumin’s surprisingly \N on top of things... I love it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.81,0:10:19.52,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.14,0:10:26.40,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,Grabbing hold of your heart!{vaguely Nanjamoish phrasing} \N There’s no bread I can’t grip!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.40,0:10:30.61,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,Hey! Manager Tong \N of Bakery Tongri-La here!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.61,0:10:34.28,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,Are you all tong-ing?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.74,0:10:36.16,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.16,0:10:37.91,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,So this is the requester...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.91,0:10:43.21,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,I’m so happy that you came, \N Ms. Gurumin{Honorifics note: Gurumin-san}, tong!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.25,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Ooh! Those’re some real \N bread-lookin’ Pokémon, ain’t they?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.63,0:10:52.26,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,This is Puppymocchi! \N The same as my father’s partner!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.80,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Uhh, and this little one...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.64,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,That’s Bowtzel with \N its Well-Baked Body, y’hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.64,0:10:59.60,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,Always on point! {Sasuga. line}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.60,0:11:05.90,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,When I announced on social media that Ms. Gurumin{Honorifics note: Gurumin-san} \N and Miniguru{Honorifics note: Miniguru-san} were coming, the replies went wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.48,0:11:09.06,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,Huh? And where is Miniguru{Honorifics note: Miniguru-san} today?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.06,0:11:12.32,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Oh... Uh... It’ll be here later!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.40,0:11:19.45,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,Well then, the Gurumin baking event \N will be at three o’clock,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.45,0:11:23.50,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,so go and enjoy \N the Bread Fest ‘til then, tong!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.29,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,That manager was quite the character...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.80,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Is this event really going to go okay...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.30,0:11:34.97,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,That smells good!{ii nioi}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.55,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Let’s get something to eat \N while we’re here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.77,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,They’ve got Pupurin bread!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.77,0:11:47.02,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It says this is \N Mitsuhoney Honeymitsu bread!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.56,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And these are Mimiroll ear{mimi}-rolls!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.19,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Cherrimbo!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.28,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Ooh! Denjimushi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.28,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,They’ve even got Fuwante!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.32,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Harimarron sandwiches!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.95,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,They all look so good!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.91,0:12:01.58,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.24,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,It’s Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.83,0:12:07.08,Main,Girl A,0,0,0,,Wow! They’re like real Pikachu cheeks!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.83,0:12:13.17,Main,Girl B,0,0,0,,Ooh! A Pikachu! \N He’s doing a cheek pose!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.80,Main,Girls,0,0,0,,{\i1}How cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.72,0:12:19.84,Main,Girls,0,0,0,,{\i1}How cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.52,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,It says these are \N Sadaija chocolate cornets.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.81,0:12:32.15,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What a line! They’re popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.11,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We should line up, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.95,0:12:41.53,Main,Vendor,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, I just sold the last one.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.95,Main,Two persons,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.58,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Aww... What a shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.58,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Then let’s get something else...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.58,0:12:50.67,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,I wanted... Sadaija...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.96,Main,Vendor,0,0,0,,I’m sorry. \N After you came all this way...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.96,0:12:58.34,Main,Dad,0,0,0,,They’re sold out. There’s nothing they can do. \N Let’s get something else.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.38,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,I wanted {\i1}this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.73,Main,Vendor,0,0,0,,What a pickle...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.60,Main,Vendor,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that...?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.73,Main,Vendor,0,0,0,,So I {\i1}did{\i0} have one more!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.61,Main,Vendor,0,0,0,,Okay, here you go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.36,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.91,Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.91,0:13:23.24,Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Isn’t that great?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.07,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.13,0:13:37.09,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Ooh! The Denjimushi bread is steamed bread!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.13,0:13:37.09,Main,TL Note,0,0,0,,{\c0\3c&HFFFFFF\fscx80\fscy80\blur4.5\pos(1290,957)}mushi
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.80,0:13:43.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Whoa! The Pupurin bread’s \N got jiggly pudding inside!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.64,0:13:51.39,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,This Biriridama pizza’s so spicy, \N it’s zapping my tongue!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.44,Main,Girl C,0,0,0,,I can’t wait to meet Miniguru!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.44,0:14:00.65,Main,Girl D,0,0,0,,Right? I even made some cheering gear!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.65,0:14:01.53,Main,Girl C,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.91,0:14:04.32,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Dot?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.74,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Maybe we should \N head over early and prepare.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.79,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.29,0:14:10.87,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Wanival, Metamon.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.58,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh? Metamon?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.46,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Metamon’s not here?!
Comment: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:23.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.89,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.39,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.48,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Where could it have gotten...?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.94,0:14:38.40,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Dot, you go on ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.57,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.24,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Don’t worry! \N We’ll bring Metamon over by three o’clock!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.24,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.37,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Time to dig in!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.01,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.97,0:15:07.26,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.68,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Trash can, trash can... \N Ah, here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.31,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.19,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.49,0:15:32.66,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.42,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh? What’s going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.21,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,There’s so many Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.72,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Metamon bread?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.47,0:15:54.31,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Gah... That’s going to make \N looking for Metamon even harder!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.77,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Seen it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.77,0:16:01.23,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,No. How could it get lost \N right when we need it...?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.03,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Is it {\i1}really{\i0} lost?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.03,0:16:03.57,Main,Roy Ult,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.15,0:16:07.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Metamon only recently \N came aboard the Brave Asagi...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.82,0:16:11.70,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Maybe it found someplace better, \N and went off somewhere...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.08,0:16:14.83,Main,Baker,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.54,0:16:18.92,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.92,0:16:23.21,Main,Baker,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s... The pizza oven wasn’t working properly, \N and I didn’t know what to do...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.26,Main,Baker,0,0,0,,Huh? There’s another oven \N right out here...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.09,0:16:33.51,Main,Baker,0,0,0,,What a relief! \N Now I can cook more Biriridama pizzas!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.77,Main,Baker,0,0,0,,It was a Metamon! \N It gave me such a scare!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.86,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Metamon? Where is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.86,0:16:49.03,Main,Baker,0,0,0,,I couldn’t say. \N It all happened so suddenly...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.03,0:16:53.78,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I wonder... Why would Metamon \N want to transform into that...?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.91,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Gotta be for a prank.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.91,0:17:00.50,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Never mind that. If it’s transformed \N into something, we’ll never find it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.30,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,If we want to find \N a transformed Metamon...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.71,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That’s the only way!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.34,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yamirami! Shadow Cross!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.34,0:17:13.26,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Nyoom-nyoom-nyoom-nyoom...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.26,0:17:16.01,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Loudbone! Nose Lantern!{Not a real move}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.14,0:17:20.02,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! Eye Flowers!{Not a real move}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.27,0:17:26.94,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Nyoom-nyoom-nyoom-nyoom...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.45,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Whoa! What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.45,0:17:36.95,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,That’s it! Over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.67,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We’ve been looking for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.54,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,There’s no time!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.59,0:17:53.09,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,Bakery Tongri-La presents...! \N To commemorate the baking of Gurumin bread...!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.72,0:17:57.39,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,A Gurumin and Miniguru With Friends Showtime!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.39,0:18:00.52,Main,Manager Tong,0,0,0,,Starting now, tong!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.94,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Yo-ssu! Spinnin’-‘n’-groovin’!{090}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.94,0:18:14.03,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,All you bread superfans out there! \N Comin’ in for a min?{minmin}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.57,0:18:17.45,Main,Girl C,0,0,0,,Eek! It’s Gurumin!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.95,Main,Girl D,0,0,0,,Gurumin!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.58,Main,Girl D,0,0,0,,Huh? Where’s Miniguru?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.37,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Minmin!{minmin}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.37,0:18:27.09,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Yay! Minmin!{minmin}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.17,0:18:27.09,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ack! They’ve already started!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.09,0:18:29.42,Main,Girl C,0,0,0,,Is Miniguru not coming...?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.42,0:18:33.26,Main,Girl D,0,0,0,,Even though I brought Miniguru \N cheering gear and everything...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.22,0:18:34.97,Main,Fan A,0,0,0,,Where’s Miniguru?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.97,0:18:36.35,Main,Fan B,0,0,0,,Isn’t it here yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.35,0:18:40.10,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Th-The Gurumin bread \N will be done any moment now!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.85,Main,Fan C,0,0,0,,Where’s Miniguru?{Sounds like Go}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.37,Main,Fans,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.08,0:19:04.29,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Y’all take a min to start jammin’ \N with a countdown! Here we go!{minmin}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.29,0:19:07.29,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,The Gurumin bread will be baked \N and ready in five seconds!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.29,0:19:08.29,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.63,Main,Fans,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.17,Main,Gurumin & Fans,0,0,0,,{\i1}One!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.42,0:19:19.05,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Ta-dough! \N The Gurumin bread’s finished!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.22,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Ack!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.56,Main,Girl C,0,0,0,,Whoa! Miniguru!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.27,Main,Girl D,0,0,0,,Miniguru!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.98,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Huh? Miniguru?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.32,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Miniguru!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.32,0:19:35.57,Main,Fan,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.57,0:19:39.49,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Ta-dough! \N Time to perform the Miniguru Dance!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.46,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Miniguru! Guru-Gurumin!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.46,0:19:50.59,Main,Girls,0,0,0,,Eek! So cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.59,0:19:54.55,Main,Fans,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Miniguru! Miniguru! Guru-Gurumin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.55,0:19:59.55,Main,Fans,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Miniguru! Miniguru! Guru-Gurumin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.06,Main,Fans,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Miniguru! Miniguru! Guru-Gurumin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.06,0:20:04.02,Main,Fans,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Miniguru! Miniguru! Guru-Gurumin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.55,0:19:57.09,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,So this is the Miniguru Dance!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.02,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I’ve got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.02,0:20:05.18,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Got what?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.18,0:20:08.98,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Metamon wasn’t transforming \N in order to play pranks...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.98,0:20:13.32,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I think it just wanted to bring joy to people \N who were sad or troubled! {please line}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.16,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah! You’re right!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.09,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Manager Tong gave me some souvenirs!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.97,0:20:39.59,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,They look good!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.34,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,There’s even Miniguru bread in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.34,0:20:43.85,Main,Molly,0,0,0,,Ooh, they’re well made!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.93,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Time to dig in!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.73,0:20:49.02,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Mmm, delish!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.98,0:20:54.36,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,The event was a huge success! \N Great work out there, Dot!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.36,0:20:56.23,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I owe it all to Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.49,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Thank you, Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.53,0:21:03.99,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,And I’m so glad \N all of {\i1}you{\i0} were there, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.66,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Surfugo!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.16,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Dekanuchan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.71,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.71,0:21:12.38,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.51,0:21:23.55,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Aren’t you going to eat yours, Liko?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.27,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Look at how cute it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.02,0:21:30.77,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’d be such a waste! \N I can’t possibly eat it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.77,0:21:32.94,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I can eat it for ya, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.94,0:21:33.98,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.98,0:21:38.65,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha...?! Masquernya!
Comment: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie A}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.58,0:21:47.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Friede here!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.92,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s time to Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.59,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Today’s topic is Bowtzel!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.59,0:21:59.30,Main,Friede,0,0,20,,The pleasant aroma that emanates \N from its body has a certain effect.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.30,0:22:01.51,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,But do you know what that effect is?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.09,0:22:06.47,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,See the answer after the commercials!
Comment: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:06.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:36.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie B}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.36,0:23:42.28,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Time to announce \N the correct answer!{正解を発表しよう}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.28,0:23:43.86,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,The answer is...{答えは…}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.86,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,B: It makes wheat grow!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.57,0:23:49.99,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Farming villages have treasured \N this Pokémon since the days of yore!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.45,0:23:54.79,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What a nice smell, just like bread...{ii nioi}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.79,0:23:56.04,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Comment: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.54,0:24:03.21,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,So this is a Unite Battle...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.21,0:24:07.72,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Yeah, they’re heated battles where \N Pokémon and trainers fight as one!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.72,0:24:10.05,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That means teamwork’s important.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.05,0:24:12.18,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Isn’t the other team too strong?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.18,0:24:14.06,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I’ll turn the tables on ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.06,0:24:15.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Everyone, let’s do our best!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.93,0:24:17.19,Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.19,0:24:20.61,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And so, to be continued \N next time on Pocket Monsters!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.61,0:24:22.07,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.07,0:24:25.03,Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,{\i1}READY GO! Unite Battle!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.32,0:24:28.82,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn’t that Pokémon...?
